txt.en: 'You have left the Gundabad forces weakened. They will need to rebuild their ranks before attempting to retake Thikil-gundu.'

'Thikil-gundu is not quite as dangerous as it once was, but new forces threaten to take it over. There are ancient tomes contained within that could prove to be very valuable to us.

'Would you be willing to go back in to Thikil-gundu once again?'

<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
'You must head to Thikil-gundu at once!'

Deep within the Grey Mountains lies Thikil-gundu. It is home to tomes of knowledge, long thought lost.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest has a one hour time limit. The timer will begin upon accepting the quest.</rgb>
You should return to to Stráhek the Stout in Skarháld and let him know of your success.
